TI  - Integrating AI-Driven Large Language Models Tools for Enhanced Problem-Solving and Troubleshooting in Automation of Manufacturing Systems Education
T2  - ADVANCING LEARNING FACTORIES: ENABLING FUTURE-READY SKILLS, VOL 1
