TI  - Development of a Virtual Reality for Physiology Education
T2  - BALNEO AND PRM RESEARCH JOURNAL
LA  - English
KW  - Virtual Reality (VR)
KW  - Exercise Physiology
KW  - MOOCs
KW  - Immersive Learning
