TI  - Design and research of automated teaching feedback and student performance assessment system based on NLP
T2  - JOURNAL OF COMPUTATIONAL METHODS IN SCIENCES AND ENGINEERING
LA  - English
KW  - NLP
KW  - automated teaching feedback
KW  - student performance assessment
KW  - personalized learning
