TI  - Advancing public health competencies: a practice-driven pedagogical reform integrating case studies, fieldwork, and digital simulation
T2  - FRONTIERS IN EDUCATION
LA  - English
KW  - case-based teaching
KW  - virtual simulation
KW  - multidimensional evaluation system
KW  - learning engagement
KW  - public health education
