TI  - Augmented reality as an educational tool in an informal setting: learning about coral reef ecology in a public aquarium
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF SCIENCE EDUCATION PART B-COMMUNICATION AND PUBLIC ENGAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - GAMIFICATION
KW  - GENDER
KW  - GAMES
