TI  - Artificial Intelligence in Orthopedic Medical Education: A Comprehensive Review of Emerging Technologies and Their Applications
T2  - INTERNATIONAL MEDICAL EDUCATION
LA  - English
KW  - AI and MR in orthopedic education
KW  - AI-powered platforms
KW  - personalized learning
