TI  - Digital immersion technologies transform agricultural learning: a study of interactive educational platforms among rural Colombian university students
T2  - RESEARCH IN SCIENCE & TECHNOLOGICAL EDUCATION
LA  - English
KW  - Virtual reality
KW  - digital learning
KW  - rural education
