TI  - Short-Term Gains, Long-Term Gaps: The Impact of GenAI and Search Technologies on Retention
T2  - ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE IN EDUCATION: POSTERS AND LATE BREAKING RESULTS, WORKSHOPS AND TUTORIALS, INDUSTRY AND INNOVATION TRACKS, PRACTITIONERS, DOCTORAL CONSORTIUM, BLUE SKY, AND WIDEAIED, AIED 2025, PT II
LA  - English
