TI  - Emotional Engagement and Teaching Innovations for Deep Learning and Retention in Education: A Literature Review
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ADVANCED COMPUTER SCIENCE AND APPLICATIONS
LA  - English
KW  - Emotional engagement
KW  - pedagogical recall
KW  - long-term knowledge retention
