TI  - Virtual Reality as an Educational Tool for Renewable Energy Awareness: A Literature Review
T2  - 2025 INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE ON SMART APPLICATIONS, COMMUNICATIONS AND NETWORKING, SMARTNETS
LA  - English
CP  - 7th International Conference on Smart Applications Communications and Networking-SMARTNETS-Annual
