TI  - Tacit knowledge management strategies of small- and medium-sized enterprises: An overview
T2  - SOUTH AFRICAN JOURNAL OF INFORMATION MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - tacit knowledge
KW  - SECI model
KW  - knowledge management
KW  - small and medium-sized enterprises
