TI  - Enhancing Engineering Education Through LLM-Driven Adaptive Quiz Generation: A RAG-Based Approach
T2  - 2024 IEEE FRONTIERS IN EDUCATION CONFERENCE, FIE
LA  - English
CP  - 2024 Frontiers in Education Conference
KW  - AI quiz generation
