TI  - The Impact of ChatGPT on student learning experience in Higher STEM Education: A Systematic Literature Review
T2  - 2024 21ST INTERNATIONAL CONFERENCE ON INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY BASED HIGHER EDUCATION AND TRAINING, ITHET
LA  - English
