TI  - Evaluation of the Effectiveness of Traditional Training vs. Immersive Training A Case Study of Building Safety and Emergency Training
T2  - EXTENDED REALITY, PT IV, XR SALENTO 2024
LA  - English
CP  - International Conference on Extended Reality (XR Salento)
KW  - virtual reality
KW  - building evacuation training
