TI  - Design and evaluation of a serious game for teaching nanotechnologies in pharmacy education
T2  - PHARMACY EDUCATION
LA  - English
KW  - Nanotechnology
KW  - Pharmaceutical education
KW  - Pharmaceutical technology
KW  - Serious game
