TI  - The Great Resignation: the great knowledge exodus or the onset of the Great Knowledge Revolution?
T2  - JOURNAL OF KNOWLEDGE MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Human capital
KW  - Employee turnover
KW  - Knowledge loss
KW  - The Great Resignation
KW  - Knowledge-based view of the firm
